This python script focuses on building a movie recommendation system, a movie recommendation system can recommend a movie based on three critertia which are a) Content Based recommendations, b) Popularity Based recommendations, and c) Collaborative Based recommendations.
I loaded the data, filled its null strings, selected relevant features for recommendation.
Used Tfidf vectorizer for converting text data into feature vectors. Then used cosine similarity for measuring similarity.
Imported difflib for comparing text and sequences.
